The Treasure of the Joons
The wise man Tui-Len managed to open a secret cave in the valley of the Two Rivers. In this place, the Joons hid the armor of one of their heroes, and enchanted the tomb with an ancient amulet. Now the spell has been lifted, and the armor can be taken.
#subobj 1
Take the key
The door to the armory room is locked. You need to find the key with which you can open the door.
#subobj 2
Use the key
To open the door you need to turn on the altar in the northwest room.
#subobj 3
Take the treasure
The items lie in the sarcophagus in the eastern room.